  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Increase in fuel prices",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "Ceylon Petroleum Corporation (CEYPETCO) has increased fuel prices from 2.00 am on Sunday (26).",
        "Accordingly, the new price of 92 octane petrol per liter is 470 rupees.",
        "The price of 95 octane petrol per liter has been increased by 100 rupees. The new price of 95 octane petrol per liter is 550 rupees.",
        "The price of a liter of auto diesel has been increased by 60 rupees and the new price of a liter is 460 rupees.",
        "The price of a liter of super diesel has been increased by 75 rupees. The price of a liter of super diesel is 520 rupees.",
        "Meanwhile, the Ceylon IOC has also increased fuel prices following the Ceylon Petroleum Corporation's increase in fuel prices.",
        "The price of 92 octane petrol per liter has been increased by 50 rupees. Accordingly, the new price of 92 octane petrol per liter is 470 rupees.",
        "The new price of a liter of 93 octane petrol is 500 rupees.",
        "Meanwhile, the new price of 95 octane petrol per liter is 550 rupees."
      ],
